{
  "id": "adv_card_ngs_12_01",
  "title": "伊吹渚",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ、資料整理も大体終わったな……\nもうこんな時間か……少し休憩しようかな",
      "startTime": 5.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 10.3466671626
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "小休憩にケーキはどうですか？\n今日もお疲れ様です、{user}さん",
      "startTime": 13.6133338292,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 233.33333330000096,
          "startTime": 10.5800004959
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "お、丁度小腹が空いてたんだ\nありがとう、渚……渚！？　いつからここに！？",
      "startTime": 19.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 23.3000006676
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "十五分くらい前からですかね。集中していたので\n待っている間に差し入れ買って来ちゃいました",
      "startTime": 27.6333340009,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 30.9333340009
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうだったのか。すぐに気が付けなくて申し訳ない\nそれに差し入れまでわざわざ……",
      "startTime": 35.470834144,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7133.332665800001,
          "startTime": 38.0666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "おや、ケーキの箱に何か入っているな……\nこれは……学園祭のチケット？",
      "startTime": 42.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 866.6666667000059,
          "startTime": 43.6666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 46.8679173153
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "サプライズです！　{user}さん\n星見高校のOBでしたよね、ぜひ遊びに来て下さい",
      "startTime": 49.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 54.9345839819
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "校長先生が事務所の人を呼んでいいと言っていたので\n優ちゃんと瑠依ちゃんも誘ってるんですよ",
      "startTime": 59.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 61.9012506486
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "それは賑やかな学園祭になりそうだな。……しかし\n校長先生か。そういえば麻奈の熱心なファンだったな",
      "startTime": 66.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "なんだか安心したよ。今も相変わらずアイドルが\n好きみたいでさ。よし、分かった、俺も遊びに行こう",
      "startTime": 75.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 80.7913865409
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、きっと琴乃ちゃんも喜びます！\nあと、そのことで一つお願いがあるんです",
      "startTime": 84.8913865409,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 89.2580532076
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "学園祭で琴乃ちゃんと一緒に\n体育館のステージに立たせてほしいんです！",
      "startTime": 91.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "それこそ麻奈みたいに、か\n構わないが、それも校長先生の頼みなのか？",
      "startTime": 98.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 102.062770049
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、これは琴乃ちゃんと私からのお願いです\n琴乃ちゃん、今、学園祭の実行委員として頑張ってて",
      "startTime": 106.6294367156,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 111.3627710662
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "そんな中、クラスの友達から、せっかくなら私達に\nライブをしてほしい、って声が上がってるんです",
      "startTime": 115.6961043996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "先生や事務所に許可を取らなきゃいけないし、やるなら\nやるで準備もあって大変になるとは思うんですが……",
      "startTime": 122.7627649627,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 127.5294316294
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん、ライブの話になった時、満更でもなくて\n……というか、凄く嬉しそうだったので",
      "startTime": 133.0294316294,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 136.1294316294
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "なるほどな。実行委員としても、アイドルとしても\n学園祭を盛り上げたいってことか",
      "startTime": 140.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "はい。麻奈さんも立ったステージですし\n学校やお友達のためにも、って張り切ってるんですよ",
      "startTime": 145.9459168754,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 150.0125835421
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "中学生の頃とは違って、学校の行事に積極的に関わって\nそのおかげか、クラスのみんなとも仲良くなれてて……",
      "startTime": 155.4792502088,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01-ngs013.m4a",
      "text": "とってもいい機会だと思うんです。今、ライブが\n出来れば、もっとみんなとの距離が縮まるはずですし",
      "startTime": 163.6125835421,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 167.7125937147
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな。俺の時も大変ではあったが\n渚がこうしてフォローしているなら安心だ",
      "startTime": 171.4333435059,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "ライブの件、任せてくれ。当日やれるように動いておく\nそれともし必要だったら、OBとして相談に乗るぞ",
      "startTime": 179.2666768392,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 183.0217545513
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます。お礼と言ってはなんですが\n当日は張り切ってお給仕させていただきますね！",
      "startTime": 186.888421218,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "お給仕？　聞きなれない言葉が聞こえたな……\n当日一体何をするつもりなんだ……？",
      "startTime": 195.7000101726,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 198.657196999
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01-ngs015.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、きっとびっくりしますよ\n私達、実はクラスの出し物で――",
      "startTime": 202.7238636657,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――学園祭当日",
      "startTime": 206.837190732,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 208.3905303323
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 208.4905221943
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 208.7238636657
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01-ngs016.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さーん！\nこっちですよ、こっちー！",
      "startTime": 210.7361725984,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "その姿……本当に『猫耳メイド喫茶』をしているんだな\n似合ってはいるが……店の外でもその格好なのか？",
      "startTime": 218.7000101726,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 223.2533562982
    },
    {
